data.meta_description: Robert Washington was born in the year 1440 in Wharton, Lancashire, England. He was married in the year 1464 in Warton, Lancashire, England to Elizabeth Westfield, they had 6 children. He died in the year 1528 in Warton, Lancashire, England. This information is part of Speake-Moody-Gates-Gochenour-Washington Family Tree by Kenneth L. Gochenour on Genealogy Online.
